# Data & Prisma Rules

PostgreSQL is system of record. Redis is cache/queue/lock only — never durable business truth. Search indexes are rebuildable projections. Media bytes in S3; metadata in DB.

## Prisma

- Every schema change = migration
- UUID/ULID public IDs
- Named indexes for hot paths
- Soft delete only when PRD requires recoverability

## Money & inventory

- Integer paise (or Decimal) — never float
- Reservations explicit; release on cancel/fail payment
- No implicit negative stock

## Idempotency keys required for

checkout/place order · payment webhooks · campaign award · payout/writer payment release
